    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present an exemplary specimen of automotive excellence. This vehicle remains in a state of preservation that mirrors its original delivery, featuring a flawless exterior finish and an interior cabin devoid of any perceptible wear. Meticulously maintained to the highest standards, this unit represents a rare opportunity for the discerning buyer to acquire a vehicle of unrivaled caliber. Every mechanical system has been vetted for absolute performance, ensuring that its next owner receives a vehicle that is truly beyond reproach.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
